results.description:
Come be a part of the 1st Salesforce Saturday/Trailhead meetup in Den Haag! This meetup is for anyone interested in learning all things Salesforce. It doesn't matter if you are a newbie or a seasoned veteran, we are here to have fun and learn at the same time. We will start at approximately 09:30, but we get it if your not a morning person. Feel free to come and go whenever you want. During this first meetup, we will also discuss possible locations and frequency of future meetups.

Don't forget your laptop!

Please free to share this meetup with your colleagues and/or friends.
